title: Tutorial
---
Jeez what a jerk.
Now, you don't want to work this shift don't you?
Let me tell you how to escape AEKI
Use WASD or Arrow Keys to move around
Avoid being detected by the customers, that yellow cone is their field of view
Try your best not to be spotted or you'll have to actually do your job!
Before you can leave through the doors, you need to find 2 keys.
Search all over the store in order to find them.
Once you find both keys you can head to the exit and move onto the main floor of the store.
Then you must collect 4 keys this time in order to escape for good.
Don't take too long though,
You have 5 minutes for each level to get out before your boss starts checking the cameras.
Good luck!

